<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What is parent consultation?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Parent consultation is educational and strategic guidance focused on equipping parents with tools to support their child's development, manage behaviors, and navigate school systems. It is not individual therapy for the child.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Do you provide medical diagnosis?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">NeuroNest provides parent guidance, educational resources, developmental support planning, report review support, school guidance, and between-session parent support programs. Regulated services are provided only within the professional scope, credentials, and legal requirements of the professional and client location.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">What happens in a parent guidance session?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We discuss your child's current challenges, review any relevant reports or feedback, and work collaboratively to form a structured, actionable support plan for home or school.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-navy mb-2">Can you help with my child's IEP?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, we offer school consultation services to help parents understand the IEP process, prepare for meetings, and communicate effectively with educators to ensure appropriate accommodations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <a href="/faqs" class="text-brand-navy font-bold hover:text-blue-700 inline-flex items-center">
        Read all FAQs
